title: Mega Buzz: Which Familiar Face Is Returning to SVU for Sweeps?
text: Mega Buzz: Which Familiar Face Is Returning to SVU for Sweeps? Tuesday, 20 October 2015 (13 minutes ago) B.D. Wong will reprise his role as psychiatrist Dr. George Huang on an episode scheduled to air this November, TVGuide.com has learned exclusively. The episode returns to the case from the show's 300th episode, in which Benson (Mariska Hargitay) solved a child abduction that had haunted her for more than a decade. Since leaving SVU, Wong starred on the short-lived Awake and most recently played a pivotal guest spot on USA's summer breakout Mr. Robot.
